title: Lookahead-based algorithms for anytime induction of decision trees
window: LSID3 produces classifiers of higher accuracy than C4.5. For the more difficult concepts, the advantage of LSID3 is substantial. However, for some datasets, such as Breast Cancer and Monks-3, C4.5 produces trees that are both smaller and more accurate.
